Enum MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION

    public static enum MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION
extends java.lang.Enum<MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION>
    The set of event definitions.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AUTOMATIC
      Automatic value: selects the criteria of satellite center for non-mutual events (although strictly the event starts before and ends later), and limb criteria for mutual events (neglecting penumbra).
      AUTOMATIC_FOR_DRAWING
      Automatic value for drawing purposes: selects the criteria of satellite limb for transits (including penumbra, so it is not exactly equal to satellite limb mode) and entire satellite for occultations, and satellite limb for mutual events.
      ENTIRE_SATELLITE
      The event starts/ends when the entire satellite starts/ends transiting the secondary body's limb.
      SATELLITE_CENTER
      The event starts/ends when the center of the satellite starts/ends touching the secondary body's limb.
      SATELLITE_LIMB
      The event starts/ends when the limb/edge of the satellite starts/ends touching the secondary body.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • SATELLITE_LIMB

        public static final MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION SATELLITE_LIMB
        The event starts/ends when the limb/edge of the satellite starts/ends touching the secondary body. Equivalent to calculating the umbra in mutual phenomena.

      • SATELLITE_CENTER

        public static final MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION SATELLITE_CENTER
        The event starts/ends when the center of the satellite starts/ends touching the secondary body's limb. This option will skip some partial eclipses/occultations in mutual phenomena.

      • ENTIRE_SATELLITE

        public static final MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION ENTIRE_SATELLITE
        The event starts/ends when the entire satellite starts/ends transiting the secondary body's limb. Equivalent to totality.

      • AUTOMATIC

        public static final MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION AUTOMATIC
        Automatic value: selects the criteria of satellite center for non-mutual events (although strictly the event starts before and ends later), and limb criteria for mutual events (neglecting penumbra). Default value.

      • AUTOMATIC_FOR_DRAWING

        public static final MoonEvent.EVENT_DEFINITION AUTOMATIC_FOR_DRAWING
        Automatic value for drawing purposes: selects the criteria of satellite limb for transits (including penumbra, so it is not exactly equal to satellite limb mode) and entire satellite for occultations, and satellite limb for mutual events. Default value when rendering.
